1) How to delete file

   rm -rf fileName
   
2) How to execute scripit
   using sh or ./
   
3) How to extract tar file
   tar -xvf fileNameOftar
   
4) How to check previous entered commond
   ctrl+R
   
5) How to change permission of file?
   chmod -R 777 fileName
   
6) How to cp file and paste into another dir?
   cp fileName /c/app/use
   
   cp fileName /c/app/use/fileName

7) To search

zgrep "KEYWORD" *.gz
    
